OL,3,CMan who flushed Quran down hospital
OL,4,Ctoilet convicted of hate crimes
OL,6,FA man who threw copies of the Quran
OL,7,Fdown a toilet in a hospital prayer
OL,8,Froom and then wrote "kill Jews" on his
OL,9,Fpolice cell wall after being arrested
OL,10,Fhas been convicted of hate crimes.
OL,12,FIbhraim Iqbal was found guilty of two
OL,13,Fcounts of religiously aggravated
OL,14,Fcriminal damage and one count of
OL,15,Fcriminal damage at Leeds Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt.
