OL,3,CMan who flushed Quran down hospital
OL,4,Ctoilet convicted of hate crimes
OL,6,FIqbal, 36, targeted a prayer room at
OL,7,FSt James's Hospital in Leeds last
OL,8,FNovember, smashing a framed Islamic
OL,9,Fscripture and vandalising several
OL,10,FQurans, ripping out and burning pages,
OL,11,Fand using them to block the sink and
OL,12,Ftoilet.
OL,14,FHe then went back two weeks later and
OL,15,Fstuffed rubbish down the drains
OL,16,Fcausing them to be blocked.
