OL,3,CMan who flushed Quran down hospital
OL,4,Ctoilet convicted of hate crimes
OL,6,FAfter another attempt to get into the
OL,7,Fmulti-faith room which was locked
OL,8,Fbecause of the earlier damage, he was
OL,9,Fdetained by hospital security and then
OL,10,Farrested by West Yorkshire Police.
OL,12,FCCTV footage showed Iqbal at the
OL,13,Fhospital carrying a black bin liner
OL,14,Fwhich was later found at the scene and
OL,15,Fleaving the prayer room.
OL,17,FWhile he was in custody, Iqbal
OL,18,Frequested crayons and used them to
OL,19,Fwrite the words "kill Jews" on his
OL,20,Fcell wall.
