OL,3,CMan who flushed Quran down hospital
OL,4,Ctoilet convicted of hate crimes
OL,6,FLuke Hopkinson, of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service, said: "Ibhraim
OL,8,FIqbal carried out a deliberate and
OL,9,Fsustained campaign of hatred,
OL,10,Ftargeting both Muslim and Jewish
OL,11,Fcommunities with his actions.
OL,13,F"This comes at a time where our
OL,14,Fprosecutors are working on the highest
OL,15,Fever number of hate crime cases
OL,16,Freferred to us by police."
OL,18,F"I hope today's conviction
OL,19,Fdemonstrates the CPS's commitment to
OL,20,Ftackling religiously aggravated hate
OL,21,Fcrime."
